extends layout

block content
   .container
      h1 URL shortener API
      h2 Author: 
        a(href="https://github.com/kighting/url-shortener") Kaiting Huang
      .divider
      p.title Example usage
      p Input the URL you want to shorten after the original URL. For example: 
      code https://kt-url-shortener.herokuapp.com/https://www.google.com
      p.title Expected output is JSON
      code {original url: "https://www.google.com", short url: "https://kt-url-shortener.herokuapp.com/8170"}
      p.title Usage
      p Go to https://kt-url-shortener.herokuapp.com/8170, and it will be redirected to https://www.google.com
